This is the promo page for Marvel Zombies RP. For more information, please visit our main page.

The characters advertised are not an exclusive list, rather they are a short list of suggestions. Our intention is to maintain a rotor of characters from a variety of backgrounds. Please feel free to apply outside of the characters posted here.

summary: The world has fallen to a monstrous infection, those who remain must band together to survive.  In Upstate New York, heroes and...
caption:
The world has fallen to a monstrous infection, those who remain must band together to survive.  In Upstate New York, heroes and civilians alike are working to build a life, even in the wake of civilisation crumbling.

Marvel Zombies RP open character: Miles Morales

Moderator suggestion for this character:

Miles really misses the days when his enemies were animal themed, but he’s doing his best to be a team player now that things so much more serious.

Survivors connected to Miles:
  • Jessica Drew • Spider-Woman
  • Cindy Moon • Silk
  • Peter Parker • Spider-Man

summary: Hahahaha! The weirdest thing occurred on this fine day. Some idiot anonymous troll says “You don’t deserve Peter Parker. You...
body: Hahahaha! The weirdest thing occurred on this fine day. Some idiot anonymous troll says “You don’t deserve Peter Parker. You homophobic piece of shit. Good day” . First off all, wow! okay whatever. Shipping Peter with a girl apparently offends this individual. Second of all, why the fu** would I WANT(I’m guessing sexual meaning?) Peter??? He may be one of my favorite Marvel superheroes, but that doesn’t mean I’m attracted to him in that sense. Either this person thinks I’m a girl or they thought I have a double standard and pretty much hates me because I don’t ship spideypool or something. And finally, this probably is a Stan Lee hater, which yes. They are still triggered over this great man’s opinion about Peter being a straight man(but was still open to allowing other versions of spider-men to be different sexuality). News flash, just because I don’t agree with that whole trans gender/bisexual Peter Parker headcanon, doesn’t fucking give you the right to attack me anonymously. You people need to get your head out of your asses. And yes, the anonymous asks are turned off, for now. Until people learn to fucking behave. To the anonymous troll, I hope you realize that your one stupid question can mess things up for those who genuinely were gonna ask me interesting/good questions.
